704
01:03:56,259 --> 01:04:01,189
My employment out of doors now was tocollect the dead wood in the forest,

705
01:04:01,189 --> 01:04:06,035
bringing it in my hands or on my shoulders,or sometimes trailing a dead pine tree

706
01:04:06,035 --> 01:04:09,119
under each arm to my shed.

707
01:04:09,119 --> 01:04:16,389
An old forest fence which had seen its bestdays was a great haul for me.

708
01:04:16,389 --> 01:04:21,074
I sacrificed it to Vulcan, for it was pastserving the god Terminus.

709
01:04:21,074 --> 01:04:30,619
How much more interesting an event is thatman's supper who has just been forth in the

710
01:04:30,619 --> 01:04:36,097
snow to hunt, nay, you might say, steal,the fuel to cook it with!

711
01:04:36,097 --> 01:04:40,249
His bread and meat are sweet.

712
01:04:40,249 --> 01:04:45,809
There are enough fagots and waste wood ofall kinds in the forests of most of our

713
01:04:45,809 --> 01:04:52,579
towns to support many fires, but which atpresent warm none, and, some think, hinder

714
01:04:52,579 --> 01:04:55,047
the growth of the young wood.

715
01:04:55,047 --> 01:05:00,098
There was also the driftwood of the pond.In the course of the summer I had

716
01:05:00,098 --> 01:05:07,073
