734
01:06:48,879 --> 01:06:54,999
But I was interested in the preservation ofthe venison and the vert more than the

735
01:06:54,999 --> 01:07:03,539
hunters or woodchoppers, and as much asthough I had been the Lord Warden himself;

736
01:07:03,539 --> 01:07:05,073
and if any part was burned, though I burned

737
01:07:05,073 --> 01:07:12,669
it myself by accident, I grieved with agrief that lasted longer and was more

738
01:07:12,669 --> 01:07:19,829
inconsolable than that of the proprietors;nay, I grieved when it was cut down by the

739
01:07:19,829 --> 01:07:21,119
