792
01:12:07,065 --> 01:12:13,009
Green hickory finely split makes thewoodchopper's kindlings, when he has a camp

793
01:12:13,009 --> 01:12:18,041
in the woods.Once in a while I got a little of this.

794
01:12:18,041 --> 01:12:23,074
