799
01:12:50,043 --> 01:12:57,061
Or else, departing dream, and shadowy formOf midnight vision, gathering up thy

800
01:12:57,061 --> 01:13:02,021
skirts;By night star-veiling, and by day

801
01:13:02,021 --> 01:13:06,003
