831
01:15:40,071 --> 01:15:48,026
Though, when I had been exposed to therudest blasts a long time, my whole body

832
01:15:48,026 --> 01:15:55,045
began to grow torpid, when I reached thegenial atmosphere of my house I soon

833
01:15:55,045 --> 01:15:59,007
