857
01:18:08,074 --> 01:18:14,027
Was thy existence then too fancifulFor our life's common light,

858
01:18:14,027 --> 01:18:16,003
who are so dull?

859
01:18:16,003 --> 01:18:20,077
Did thy bright gleam mysteriousconverse hold

860
01:18:20,077 --> 01:18:27,088
With our congenial souls?secrets too bold?

861
01:18:27,088 --> 01:18:32,085
